            <img alt="This is an artist's rendering of the Boston Tea Party, showing colonists dressed up as Native Americans dumping crates of tea off ships in Boston Harbor." data-uuid="635d6d6999aa447183f62773d92a816d" src="../../img/module_4_lesson01/ms_snlese454149_794p.jpg" />
